Package org.ivoa.dm.stc.coords

Class Point

java.lang.Object
org.ivoa.dm.stc.coords.Coordinate
org.ivoa.dm.stc.coords.Point
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulations
Direct Known Subclasses:
CartesianPoint, GenericPoint, LonLatPoint
@Embeddable @VoDml(id="coords:Point", role=dataType) public abstract class Point extends Coordinate implements org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulations
Multi-dimensional spatial coordinate. The Point MUST refer to a spatial coordinate system (SpaceSys) which associates the point with corresponding coordinate domain space and frame metadata. dataType: Point
